Introduction

LIMELIGHT (also stylized as LIMΞLIGHT) was a three-member sub-unit of the girl group MADEIN under 143 Entertainment. The unit consisted of members MiU, Suhye, and Gaeun.

They released the pre-debut EP "Limelight" on September 29, 2022, before making their official debut as a trio on February 17, 2023, with the EP "Love & Happiness".

On January 11, 2024, LIMELIGHT released their third EP titled "Last Dance", which was marketed as the group's last release as a trio as the group plans to reorganize and add more members.
